02:03:21,494 --> 02:03:24,314
but the nucleation of submarines

3394
02:03:24,314 --> 02:03:25,294
is very rare.

3395
02:03:26,194 --> 02:03:27,834
It doesn't happen very often.

3396
02:03:27,854 --> 02:03:29,294
It doesn't happen very often and very frequently.

3397
02:03:29,634 --> 02:03:32,474
And so most submarines will last a long time

3398
02:03:32,474 --> 02:03:33,914
without bending into a middle one.

3399
02:03:35,274 --> 02:03:39,334
So we found no evidence in the cosmic microwave background

3400
02:03:39,334 --> 02:03:40,634
for a collision like this.

3401
02:03:40,934 --> 02:03:41,494
None.

3402
02:03:41,574 --> 02:03:42,114
There's no evidence.

3403
02:03:42,354 --> 02:03:43,534
It's probably not going to be there.

3404
02:03:43,834 --> 02:03:45,314
So the only question is then,

3405
02:03:45,314 --> 02:03:46,894
what other possible kinds

3406
02:03:46,894 --> 02:03:52,194
of signatures could there be for the physics that

3407
02:03:52,194 --> 02:03:53,654
goes into this kind of theory?

3408
02:03:54,734 --> 02:03:55,514
It's hard.

3409
02:03:56,154 --> 02:03:57,834
Nobody has a really good idea.

3410
02:03:59,714 --> 02:04:01,834
That's the worst thing about this kind of idea,

3411
02:04:01,974 --> 02:04:05,354
that it just looks overwhelmingly hard to find

3412
02:04:05,354 --> 02:04:10,014
the convincing data for.

3413
02:04:11,254 --> 02:04:11,814
OK.

3414
02:04:12,694 --> 02:04:13,654
We are finished.

3415
02:04:14,474 --> 02:04:15,254
Thank you.

3416
02:04:19,494 --> 02:04:20,614
For more,

3417
02:04:20,614 --> 02:04:23,054
please visit us at stanford.edu.

